Seven time roundsie and seven time downsie

2
00:00:09,166 --> 00:00:14,833
Dances and sings we and bless with them hand

3
00:00:15,166 --> 00:00:20,833
Tears pridesy builderfools flesh for our banquets

4
00:00:21,166 --> 00:00:26,166
